subject: Hi,
body:
Hi,
How are you? I sent a mail to you, but I haven't seen your reply, It is
something very important, please reply me ok, from Olivia.

subject: Re: Hi,
body:
Hello Olivia,

I'm doing well, thank you. I apologize if I missed your previous email. Could you please provide more details about the important matter you mentioned? 

Looking forward to hearing from you.

Best wishes,
Mary
